simmasto0.util

Class C_ZoomExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • simmasto0.util.C_ZoomExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I_ConstantGerbil, I_ConstantString

    public class C_ZoomExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements I_ConstantString, I_ConstantGerbil
    Extract the input raster files (rain series or landcover) of a zoom or TPE ('très petite emprise') landscape at the desired size from the reference grid of ME ('moyenne emprise') and save the resulting files / Used in Gerbil protocol only
    Author:
    M.Sall & J.Le Fur 12.2015, rev. JLF&MS 03.2016
